item.description: That's funny. I thought Turbine was hard at work getting <a href="http://www.middle-earthonline.com/index.php?page_id=30&pagebuilder[module]=article&pagebuilder[display_item]=1" rel="nofollow">Middle Earth Online</a> up and working. That was slated for end of 2004 *looks at watch*. So, that means we should see D&D Online some time in the summer of 2007?
